column5: Any reports from west of yellow girl and north. We are staying in Sioux Narrows.Thanks

Fishing has been good for SM Bass and Walleye lately. Been very windy of late restricting how far down the lake we want to go, but last weekend we did very well jigging for walleye just north of Sunset Channel. A bit of a haul depending on your boat from Sioux Narrows though.
